title: Grateful Dead Live at Red Rocks Ampitheatre on 1984-06-13
taper: Robert Bryant patched out of Oade Brothers
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Candyman, CC Rider, Ramble On Rose, My Brother Esau, Cold Rain & Snow-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Women Are Smarter, Ship of Fools-> Let It Grow-> Drums-> The Wheel-> I Need A Miracle-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue
